## Part 6: Configure HTTPS Redirect (Optional)

Force all traffic to HTTPS:

1. **In Azure Portal** â†’ Your Static Web App
2. **Left menu** â†’ "Configuration"
3. **Add** this to your `staticwebapp.config.json`:

```json
{
  "globalHeaders": {
    "Strict-Transport-Security": "max-age=31536000"
  },
  "routes": [
    {
      "route": "/*",
      "allowedRoles": ["anonymous"]
    }
  ],
  "navigationFallback": {
    "rewrite": "/index.html"
  }
}
```

